name: 特德拉·罗杰斯
name_full: 特德拉·罗杰斯 Tedra Rogers
introduction: Tedra Rogers is an award-winning Film & TV actor whose effervescence is captivating on and off screen. Originally from Calgary, Alberta, Tedra has been in the performing arts since the age of three with an extensive 15+ year professional background in ballet, having trained at the Joffrey Ballet School and HB Studio in New York City.Tedra is known for her roles in The CW's "Charmed", "iZombie" and "Supergirl", Netflix's beloved drama "Firefly Lane" and feature film "There's Someone Inside Your House", and her recurring role in Freeform's hugely successful, record breaking, teen drama thriller series "Cruel Summer". On the big screen Tedra is known for her supporting lead role in Come True (IFC films) as well as her outstanding work starring in Here & After (Light Factory) where she enraptured audiences with her performance worldwide.When she's not on screen she can be found zooming around the city in her beloved Fiat 500 Turbo and hunting down the best spots for gluten free eats.
